<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الْبَابُ الثَّالِثُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>الْحُرُوفُ الَّتِي تُزَادُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَشْهَرُهَا الْأَلِفُ وَالْوَاوُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>زِيادَةُ الْأَلِفِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>تُزَادُ الْأَلِفُ <span style="color:#008000">(وَسَطًا)</span> فِي كَلِمَةِ <span style="color:#008000">(مائَة)</span> مُفْرَدَةً أَوْ مَرْكَبَةً كخَمسِمائَة وتِسْعِمائَة<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَتُزَادُ <span style="color:#008000">(طَرفًا)</span> فِي مَوْضِعَيْنِ:<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - بَعْدَ وَاوِ الْجَمِاعَةِ،<span style="color:#006d98"> نَحْوُ:</span> خَرَجوا وَذَهَبُوا، واخْرُجوا واذْهَبوا. لَا بَعْدَ الْوَاوِ الَّتِي هِيَ جُزْءٌ مِنَ الْفِعْلِ،<span style="color:#006d98"> نَحْوُ:</span> يَدْعُو المُصَلُّونَ،<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>